_sText:
- includes custom radar, nav mesh with place names, custom textures, etc.
- I originally made this into a hostage map, then later added about 20% more playable space with a new site area and paths, then closed off some more paths after multiple iterations due to play and balance testing.
- map works very well with 5 on 5 scrim scenarios, but also is very enjoyable with a bigger public server.

Created by dF|novalin / Brian Riggsbee
